{"tid":993071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發！] 交通警埋怨巴士入站車尾突出, 無視自己電單車阻礙巴士入站","createTime":"2019-01-23T15:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T18:13:16.000Z","uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b78e4000bd6a530957e8842de342fa9a5d59d4ca","tid":993071,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"由於中環灣仔繞道西行需繞經中環才能前往西區，因此近日警方對干諾道中西行的交通嚴陣以待，不斷趕走停留車輛。<br />\n<br />\n不過今晚有交通警員在德己利士街執勤時，卻指責巴士埋站時車尾阻礙行車線，但卻無視自己的電單車泊在巴士站後，阻礙巴士入站。<br />\n<br />\n資料及相片由麥當勞打雜提供<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkitalk.net/HKiTalk2/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=1110492&amp;aid=389501&amp;from=album&amp;page=1&amp;mobile=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkitalk.net%2FHKiTalk2%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1110492%26aid%3D389501%26from%3Dalbum%26page%3D1%26mobile%3D2&d=SNcgiO0Jsq9L6NEwCudGKXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3403cb69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkitalk.net/HKiTalk2/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=1110492&amp;aid=389501&amp;from=album&amp;page=1&amp;mobile=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P66rHCv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP66rHCv.png&h=f5a3ddfe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de999cb00475a98e643a0b17c113974e9998409b","tid":993071,"uid":202278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T18:13:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}